  "texts": [
    "We have shown that CNN outperforms classical methods when it comes to classification, detection, and prediction.",
    "Through exploiting depth and other structural modifications, CNN's learning performance has dramatically improved over time.",
    "According to recent literature, the increase in CNN performance is primarily attributable to the replacement of the conventional layer structure with blocks.",
    "The function of an auxiliary learner can be performed by a block in a network.",
    "These additional learners leverage spatial or feature-map information or even enhance input channels to increase performance."
  ],
